gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "Well, it's a pleasure to meet you, \n"
	.string "{PLAYER}! \p"
	.string "I hope you're excited to begin your \n"
	.string "Pokémon journey here in Marya! \p"
	.string "You'll be helping me conduct field \n"
	.string "research along with another bright \l"
	.string "young trainer! \p"
	.string "But don't stress too much about the \n"
	.string "work. I want you to have fun as well!\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "I'll be seeing you in my laboratory in a \n"
	.string "week at the port town of Cheriport. \p"
	.string "Until then, enjoy the all-expense paid \n"
	.string "cruise I've included for you! \p"
	.string "If you have a chance, you should try\n"
	.string "their lobster. I hear It's amazing! \p"
	.string "I look forward to seeing you in-person, \n"
	.string "{PLAYER}. \p"
	.string "May your voyage be safe and sound.\p"
	.string "$"
